" Watch Hillary Clinton\x92s Concession Speech Video
\x93Last night I congratulated Donald Trump and offered to work with him on behalf of our country. I hope that he will be a president for all of our country...
\x93I\x92m sorry that we did not win this election for the values we all share...
\x93You represent the best of America, and being your candidate has been one of the greatest honors of my life. I know how disappointed you feel, because I feel it too.... Donald Trump's Victory Speech "
